.training-form
  = bootstrap_form_for @invitation, url: team_invitations_path do |f|
    = f.collection_select(:invitee_id, @invitees, :id, :username)
    = f.hidden_field :team_id, value: team_id
    = f.submit 'Invite!', class: 'btn btn-primary btn-block'
  hr
  p The user will be notified about your invitation and a partnership will be proposed, which the invitee can either reject or accept